# Streamlit App Walkthrough (Ring Finger Boost)

## Summary
The **Ring Finger** is now boosted (more sensitive) to help with chords.

## Configuration
- **Ring Finger Threshold**: `0.05` (Easy).
- **Other Fingers Threshold**: `0.10` (Normal).
- **Smoothing**: Active (Alpha 0.7).

## How to Run
```bash
./.venv/bin/streamlit run app.py
```
Open the URL shown in the terminal (usually http://localhost:8501).
